line_1: IN Russia's frozen clime some ages since
line_2: There dwelt, historians say, a worthy prince,

line_1: A whole three hundred years compleated since
line_2: Three hundred years! re-echo'd back the prince,

line_1: I scarce have had one happy Moment since.
line_2: The Jingling noise, shed its dark Influence,

line_1: I scarce have had one happy Moment since.
line_2: On my then pleased, unwary Innocence,

line_1: Where Painters, Poets, not as since,
line_2: Were greater held than any Prince;

line_2: The Pedant Scholar, he forgot the Prince,
